text: Selena Gomez’s loved ones are becoming very concerned wih her weight. Sources are saying that the “Hands to Myself” star is "wasting away" to get herself down to a size zero dress size! Everyone’s worried that her addictive personality has been taken to the extreme in this situation, and the routines to get herself super skinny, sources claim, are very troubling.
title: Wasting Away? Selena Gomez On A Mission To Be A Size Zero!

meta_data.description: Everyone around the ‘Hands to Myself’ star is worried for her.
